</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uyrehcra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yrehcra</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/11/01 9:17:06 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.neoreality.com/archery/wolfvs.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: DOT's and stacking</span><hr size=1> I know about solo doting but can 2 or more druids stack the same dot? Also which dots of other classes stack with us? <p>Yrehcra<br>
Human Druid<br>
45th Season<br>
Legacy of Titans, Nameless<br>
<i>"How can I be out of drink when I have all these ales!"<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugorgodarkfyre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GorgoDarkfyre</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/11/01 9:20:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: DOT's and stacking</span><hr size=1> No, 2 or more druids cannot stack the same dot.<br>
All other classes dots stack with ours, however I think some rarely used debuffs don't stack with the Breath of Ro line (necro Scent of Terris if I remember well, but don't quote me on this one).<br>
 <p>[60 Hierophant] Tworgo Barkfyre (Halfling) &lt;Skyfire&gt;<BR>
[52 Reaver] Gorgo Darkfyre (Troll) &lt;Skyfire&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ustormhaven.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stormhaven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/11/01 9:24:12 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://web2.airmail.net/naomi/amalgam/forum/stormhaven.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: DOT's and stacking</span><hr size=1> Bit off topic, but the druid Ice spells won't stack either. So if a higher level player casts Ice on a mob, then a lower level druid does, it won't stick due to the SVC portion of the spell. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nilwean>nilwean</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/21/01 1:15:36 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: DOT's and stacking</span><hr size=1> All of these stack:<br>
<br>
1) One of: Stinging Swarm, Creeping Crud, Drones of Doom, Drifting Death<br>
2) Winged Death<br>
3) Flame Lick<br>
4) Immolate<br>
5) Breath of Ro<br>
6) Wrath of Nature<br>
<br>
Yes, Flame Lick, Immolate, and Breath of Ro all stack....<br>
<br>
